# 🔄 3️⃣ FULL REDEPLOY ORDER (IMPORTANT)

Deploy **in this exact order** 👇

```text
1️⃣ Zookeeper
2️⃣ Kafka
3️⃣ Redis
4️⃣ Postgres / MongoDB
