# 🧪 4️⃣ VERIFY EVERYTHING IS WORKING (ONE SCRIPT)

### 🔹 `health-check.sh`

```bash
#!/bin/bash

NS=job-scheduler

echo "📦 Pods"
kubectl get pods -n $NS -o wide

echo ""
echo "🌐 Services"
kubectl get svc -n $NS

echo ""
echo "📀 PVCs"
kubectl get pvc -n $NS

echo ""
echo "⚙️ Deployments"
kubectl get deploy -n $NS

echo ""
echo "📊 StatefulSets"
kubectl get sts -n $NS

echo ""
echo "🔥 Events (last 20)"
kubectl get events -n $NS --sort-by=.metadata.creationTimestamp | tail -20
```

Run:

```bash
chmod +x health-check.sh
./health-check.sh
```

