# 🧪 5️⃣ KAFKA MESSAGE TEST (REAL VERIFICATION)

### Produce

```bash
kubectl exec -it kafka-0 -n job-scheduler -- \
kafka-console-producer \
--bootstrap-server kafka:9092 \
--topic test-topic
```

Type message:

```
hello-from-producer
```

### Consume

```bash
kubectl exec -it kafka-1 -n job-scheduler -- \
kafka-console-consumer \
--bootstrap-server kafka:9092 \
--topic test-topic \
--from-beginning
```

✔️ If message appears → Kafka is healthy

