# 📌 6️⃣ COMMON FAILURE QUICK FIXES

### ImagePullBackOff

```bash
kubectl describe pod <pod> -n job-scheduler
```

### CrashLoopBackOff

```bash
kubectl logs <pod> -n job-scheduler --previous
```

### Kafka broker not connecting

```bash
kubectl exec -it kafka-0 -n job-scheduler -- env | grep KAFKA
```

